# Connections

On add/remove/validate: **one connection per port**; exactly one of **`targetPort`** or **`targetParameter`**; types compatible — enforce in data-model validation / `immutableUpdates`.

Replace: remove existing wire on that target, then add; never both/neither target fields set.

**Refs:** `src/data-model/validation.ts`, `immutableUpdates.ts`, `docs/user-goals/05-connections.md`, `docs/architecture/graph-and-platform-boundaries.md` (connections / graph model).
